## AI Tools Nonprofits Are Most Likely to Encounter

|Tool Type                                          |Risk Context                              |What to Check                                                                                             |
|---------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|AI-assisted job description generation             |Administrative Expert.                    |Review for FLSA classification before posting.                                                            |
|AI-assisted resume screening                       |Strategic Partner / Administrative Expert.|Require demographic parity documentation before use. Highest proxy variable risk.                         |
|AI-assisted employee handbooks and policy templates|Administrative Expert.                    |Treat as starting draft — requires attorney review before distribution.                                   |
|AI chatbots for HR policy questions                |Depends on configuration.                 |If employees ask about their employment rights, this is Employee Champion territory. Apply that checklist.|
|AI sentiment or engagement surveys                 |Change Agent.                             |Requires human interpretation before board review. Check whether individual employees are identifiable.   |
|AI scheduling or volunteer management tools        |Administrative Expert.                    |Lower risk — but volunteer/employee classification must be clear first.                                   |

